snippet.title: Gang Beasts - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Welcome to Beef City.

The silly multiplayer party game with surly gelatinous characters and brutal slapstick fight sequences Gang Beasts is coming to Nintendo Switch this fall!

Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/gang-beasts-switch/

#GangBeasts #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
